Automatic Prompt Engineer [zhou2023large] uses LLM models like InstructGPT [ouyang2022training] and instruction induction [honovich2022instruction] to generate instruction candidates which are then improved by proposing semantically similar instruction variants to achieve human-level performance.
Zhou et al. [zhou2023large] investigate the ability of LLMs, such as GPT-3, to generate high-quality prompts for a variety of tasks.